Umkhokha actor Nay Maps, real name Nkosinathi Maphalala, will release his first music single in May ahead of his full album. Following an intimate listening session with close friends, Nay Maps shared on social media that his music will reflect his personality. Not only is he a formidable actor, but Nay Maps has proven that he is a great singer as he flaunted his singing talent on a number of occasions, even when he was still part of SABC1 telenovela Uzalo. “Super excited to share this with you all, I’ll be releasing my first single soon,” he wrote.  The actor also has a thriving clothing label, Nay Maps Clothing, which he launched a few years ago. For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.